name: Fly Higher
description:
One of my collectors asked me if I've ever made an art that speaks for pain as I mostly draw something fun and joyful. Well, he's right. Truth is, I always try to be that happy girl even when I'm sad and devastated. So, in this special occasion, I really want to embrace the pain as I lately heard so many death news that broke me too.

This piece is dedicated for those who lost their loved ones. Although the stars seem dull and your night seems empty; I hope you know that you’re still surrounded by much love🤍
